    <div class="container">
      <a href="/start-team" class="btn btn-secondary back-button">&larr; Back to Steps</a>
      <p class="step-label">Step 2 of 9</p>
      <h1>Find a Coach</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Every FTC team needs an adult who can support safety, communication, and official team responsibilities.</p>
      <section class="content-section">
        <p>The coach does not need to know everything about robotics. They do need to be dependable, willing to help the team stay organized, and comfortable working with students and sponsors.</p>
        <div class="content-subsection">
          <h3>What to ask for</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Help with scheduling and meeting space</li>
            <li>Support with FIRST registration and team paperwork</li>
            <li>A safe adult contact for parents and sponsors</li>
            <li>Long-term consistency for the team</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <p><strong>Action:</strong> Talk to teachers, mentors, parents, or community leaders who are willing to help guide the team.</p>
      </section>
      <div class="step-actions">
        <a href="/start-team-step3" class="btn btn-primary">Next: Get FIRST Involved &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
